README.md
     1тЖТ# dotenv
     5тЖТDotenv is a zero-dependency module that loads environment variables from a `.env` file into [`process.env`](https://nodejs.org/docs/latest/api/process.html#process_process_env). Storing configuration in the environment separate from code is based on [The Twelve-Factor App](https://12factor.net/config) methodology.
     6тЖТ
     7тЖТ[Watch the tutorial](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YtkZR0NFd1g)
     8тЖТ
     9тЖТ&nbsp;
    10тЖТ
    11тЖТ## Usage
    13тЖТInstall it.
    14тЖТ
    15тЖТ```sh
    16тЖТnpm install dotenv --save
