   579тЖТ## Docs
   581тЖТDotenv exposes four functions:
   582тЖТ
   583тЖТ* `config`
   584тЖТ* `parse`
      тЖТтАж
   587тЖТ### Config
   589тЖТ`config` will read your `.env` file, parse the contents, assign it to
   590тЖТ[`process.env`](https://nodejs.org/docs/latest/api/process.html#process_process_env),
   591тЖТand return an Object with a `parsed` key containing the loaded content or an `error` key if it failed.
   592тЖТ
   593тЖТ```js
      тЖТтАж
   605тЖТ#### Options тАж
   607тЖТ##### path
   609тЖТDefault: `path.resolve(process.cwd(), '.env')`
